column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.

I am an AI doctor, which means I can provide advice on medical symptoms and treatments. I am not able to perform physical examinations, but I can make an educated diagnosis of what may be wrong based on your symptoms. Please let me know what symptoms you are experiencing.
I understand your boredom, however I'm unable to provide treatment advice for that issue. If you are having specific medical symptoms, please let me know what they are.
